Looks like api compatibility test has detected a change in the public TF python API.

ERROR:tensorflow:1 differences found between API and golden.
ERROR:tensorflow:Issue 1	: Change detected in python object: tensorflow.layers.BatchNormalization.

Could you confirm the change is intended, run the test in a python2 + linux setup (you may use our devel docker images) and pack the change into this pull request?
Then we will need an API review before we can merge this PR.

body:
Looks like api compatibility test has detected a change in the public TF python API.
```
ERROR:tensorflow:1 differences found between API and golden.
ERROR:tensorflow:Issue 1	: Change detected in python object: tensorflow.layers.BatchNormalization.
```

Could you confirm the change is intended, run the test in a python2 + linux setup (you may use our devel docker images) and pack the change into this pull request?
Then we will need an API review before we can merge this PR.
